channel.description:
[code]jag_archive {
   /* if dcmp_size == cmp_size, the archive is compressed as a whole */
   hdr {
       u24 dcmp_sz;
       u24 cmp_sz;
   }
   /* following data is compressed if compressed as whole */
   bdy {
       ent_tbl {
           u16 ent_cnt;
           u32 ent_id_tbl[ent_cnt];
           u32 ent_dcmp_sz_tbl[ent_cnt];
           u32 ent_cmp_sz_tbl[ent_cnt];
       }
       u1 data[dcmp_size];
   }
}[/code]

data contains the rest of the file data; if ent_dcmp_sz_tbl[ent_idx] != ent_cmp_sz_tbl[ent_idx], then entry ent_idx is compressed. the compression used is bzip without magic header.
